library(corrplot)
## corrplot 0.95 loaded
cor_matrix <- cor(
  met[, c("temp", "wind.sp", "elev", "atm.press", "rh", "dew.point")],
  use = "complete.obs",
  method = "pearson"
)
corrplot(cor_matrix, method = "color", type = "upper",
         title = "Correlation Matrix of Weather Variables",
         mar = c(0,0,2,0))
